(5, 'cnc', 'CORPORATE & COMMERCIAL', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#444956\">One of Apex Advocate\'s key practice areas is corporate and\r\ncommercial, which extends to various sectors of the economy and wide array of\r\nbusiness and transactional matters. The Firm’s experience and expertise in\r\nproviding advice on corporate and commercial contracts and joint ventures,\r\ninbound and outbound investment, regulatory and compliance, corporate\r\ngovernance, operational and structuring matters across a broad range of sectors\r\nis well recognised.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#444956\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#444956\">One of the reasons for\r\nthe strength of our practice is that the partners of the Firm have: (a)\r\nwitnessed the impact of and have helped client’s transition through the changes\r\nin the regulatory environment in India including relating to foreign\r\ninvestment; and (b) extensive experience in dealing with a broad spectrum of\r\nregulators and a variety of regulatory issues.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#444956\">Our Corporate and\r\nCommercial Expertise include:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;color:#444956\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#444956\">Drafting Commercial Agreements including E-commerce Agreements,\r\nSoftware Development Agreements, Franchise Agreements, On-Boarding Agreements,\r\nInvestment Agreements, Share-Holder Agreements, Unit-Franchise Agreements,\r\nMaster-Franchise Agreements and Brand Ambassador Agreements.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;color:#444956\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#444956\">Filing and Registration of Intellectual Properties of products\r\nsuch as Trademarks, Copyrights and Patents.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2025-04-15 12:49:50', '2025-04-15 13:46:47'),
(6, 'ip', 'INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:5.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\n18.0pt;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#0A0A0A;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;\r\npadding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Our firm is recognized for its\r\nwell-established IP practice, dedicated to protecting and enforcing the\r\nintellectual property rights of our clients. Our team of experienced IP\r\nattorneys provides strategic advice and tailored solutions to safeguard\r\ntrademarks, copyrights, designs, patents, and other intellectual property\r\nassets in India. We offer comprehensive IP protection services, including\r\nregistration, prosecution, enforcement, licensing, and litigation, to ensure\r\nthat our clients’ valuable intellectual property assets are effectively\r\nprotected and monetized.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:5.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\n18.0pt;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#0A0A0A;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\r\nnone windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#0A0A0A;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\r\nnone windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Comprehensive IP\r\nServices</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:18.0pt;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#0A0A0A;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Our\r\nfirm offers a wide range of IP services to meet the diverse needs of our\r\nclients. Whether it’s securing trademark registrations, filing copyright\r\napplications, obtaining design patents, or prosecuting patent applications, our\r\nattorneys provide expert guidance and support at every stage of the IP\r\nlifecycle. We also assist clients in drafting and negotiating IP licensing\r\nagreements, conducting IP due diligence, and enforcing their IP rights through\r\nadministrative proceedings and litigation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:18.0pt;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#0A0A0A;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">&nbsp;</span><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#0A0A0A;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Strategic\r\nIP Portfolio Management</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:18.0pt;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#0A0A0A;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Effective\r\nmanagement of intellectual property portfolios is essential for maximizing the\r\nvalue of IP assets and minimizing risks. At Apex Advocates, we work closely\r\nwith our clients to develop and implement strategic IP portfolio management\r\nstrategies tailored to their business objectives and industry dynamics. Our\r\nattorneys conduct IP audits, assess portfolio strengths and weaknesses, and\r\nformulate customized IP management plans to align with our clients’ overall\r\nbusiness goals and competitive landscape.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:18.0pt;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#0A0A0A;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">&nbsp;</span><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#0A0A0A;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;\r\nmso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">International\r\nIP Protection</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:5.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\n18.0pt;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#0A0A0A;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;\r\npadding:0cm;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">In an increasingly globalized\r\nmarketplace, protecting intellectual property rights across borders is crucial\r\nfor maintaining competitive advantage and preventing unauthorized use or\r\ninfringement. Apex Advocates offers comprehensive international IP protection\r\nservices, including filing and prosecuting international trademark and patent\r\napplications, navigating cross-border IP enforcement issues, and advising on\r\ninternational IP treaties and conventions.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2025-04-15 12:50:29', '2025-04-15 13:50:09'),
