(12, 'Myth Busted: A Verbal Agreement Has No Legal Value', 7, 9, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">MYTH:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"> “If there’s nothing in writing,\r\nit doesn’t count.”<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">FACT:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"> Verbal agreements <i>can be\r\nlegally binding</i> in India—provided they meet certain conditions.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Under the\r\n<b>Indian Contract Act, 1872</b>, an agreement becomes a contract when:<o:p></o:p></span></p><ul type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">There is an offer and\r\n     acceptance,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">The parties are competent,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">There is lawful\r\n     consideration and intent.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">While\r\nwritten contracts offer clarity and proof, <b>a verbal agreement</b>—such as an\r\noral promise to repay money or provide a service—can hold legal weight.\r\nHowever, proving it in court can be challenging.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Example:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"> If you lent money to someone and\r\nthere were witnesses or messages referring to the repayment, you may still have\r\na valid legal claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Pro Tip:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"> Always <b>document your\r\nagreements</b> in writing, especially in matters of money, property, or\r\nemployment. It prevents disputes and protects your rights.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Need help\r\nvalidating an agreement or contract? Our commercial law team can guide you.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2024-01-17 13:00:00', '2025-04-15 14:09:59', 1, 'Myth-Busted:-A-Verbal-Agreement-Has-No-Legal-Value', '8db9ae3a8a58d9a4f4ef0d75fc95a68bjpeg', 22, 'admin', 'admin'),
(13, 'New Changes in Consumer Protection Rules 2025', 3, 10, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The\r\nMinistry of Consumer Affairs has notified amendments to the <strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">Consumer Protection (E-commerce) Rules, 2025</span></strong>,\r\naimed at enhancing accountability and protecting consumer interests in digital\r\ntransactions.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">Key Highlights of the New Policy Changes:</span></strong><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">Mandatory Seller Verification:</span></strong><br>\r\nE-commerce platforms must verify all sellers before listing their products.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">Stronger Return &amp; Refund Rules:</span></strong><br>\r\nPlatforms cannot impose arbitrary return/refund timelines. The rules now\r\nmandate <strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">minimum 10-day return windows</span></strong>\r\nfor most product categories.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">No Dark Patterns:</span></strong><br>\r\nMisleading advertisements, fake scarcity tactics (like “Only 1 left!”), and\r\npre-ticked boxes have been banned.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">Data Privacy Obligations:</span></strong><br>\r\nStricter rules introduced for platforms collecting customer data—ensuring\r\ngreater compliance with data protection norms.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">Impact on Businesses:</span></strong><br>\r\nE-commerce sellers, aggregators, and digital marketers must <strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\">review their policies and contracts immediately</span></strong>\r\nto avoid penalties.<o:p></o:p></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(41, 41, 41); line-height: 1.6; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">At\r\nApex Advocates, we help businesses stay compliant with evolving legal standards\r\nand consumer policies. Talk to us to review your online terms of service.<o:p></o:p></p>', '2024-01-18 13:00:00', '2025-04-15 14:11:56', 1, 'New-Changes-in-Consumer-Protection-Rules-2025', 'cd588832d8debf1304b64d343bb7f46d.jpg', 8, 'admin', 'admin');

